		left: -8px;
		top: 2px;
	}
	
	.nametext,
	.pricetext {
		display: block;
	}
	
	.nametext {
		white-space: nowrap;
		display: block;
		width: 112%;
		color: gray;
		overflow: hidden;
	}
	
	.goodsgroupname {
		width: 85%;
		/*height: 20px;*/
		line-height: 20px;
		padding-left: 10px;
	}
	
	.goodsgroupname p {
		margin: 0;
		padding: 0;
		font-size: 1.2rem;
		display: inline-block;
	}
	
	.collect {
		display: inline-block;
		/*margin-top: 12%;*/
